### HTML viewer page (rendered via Jet template)
GET http://localhost:8080/

### List registered languages (from registry)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/languages

### PHP call graph (DOT format)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=php

### Python call graph (DOT format)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=python

### Per-file call graph
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=php&file=Router.php

### Per-file structure graph
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=php&file=Controllers/UserController.php&type=structure

### Per-file external calls graph
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=python&file=core/pipeline.py&type=external

### List PHP source files
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files?lang=php

### List Python source files
GET http://localhost:8080/api/files?lang=python

### --- Error cases ---

### Missing lang parameter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph

### Unknown language (resolved via registry)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph?lang=ruby
